  <brief_title>The Prognostic Value of Interim PET/CT After 2 Cycles of Chemotherapy in Predicting Progression of Non Hodgkins Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Prognostic Value of Early Interim PET/CT for Prediction of Progression Free Survival of Patients With Aggressive B Cells Non Hodgkin Lymphoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
